Content:
Can't recommend Stylus enough. Some features not found on less or scss: optional colons, semicolons and braces and referencing properties:<p><pre><code>  body
    color black
    a
      color @color
</code></pre>
will compile to<p><pre><code>  body{
    color: black;
    a{
      color: black;
    }
  }</code></pre>
